            Description = "example description",

                    "JSON",

}

## Import


Backup Report Plan can be imported using the `id` which corresponds to the name of the Backup Report Plan, e.g.,

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:backup/reportPlan:ReportPlan test <id>
```
